OL,7,FJohn Stevenson, MP for Carlisle has
OL,8,Fspoken out after calling for the
OL,9,FSpeaker of the House of Commons to be
OL,10,Fremoved from his position.
OL,12,FIt follows last night around the
OL,13,Fdebate led by the SNP on the Israel-
OL,14,FGaza conflict.
OL,16,FMr Stevenson was one of the first MPs
OL,17,Fin a growing list to sign the
OL,19,FHe told ITV Border: "The role of the
OL,20,Fspeaker is extremely important in our
OL,21,Fparliamentary system.
